11
00:00:49,491 --> 00:00:52,702
We're supposed to figure out the meaning through the context,

12
00:00:52,702 --> 00:00:54,562
but that's not as easy as it seems.

13
00:00:54,562 --> 00:00:56,558
After taking an exam,

14
