to solve the question."

17
00:01:05,538 --> 00:01:08,326
We all know that being flustered is not the real problem.

18
00:01:08,326 --> 00:01:10,220
This grammar we use in these kinds of situations

19
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:12,855
is called the "Too...to" method.

20
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:17,543
Oh. 
 Hello.

21
