48
00:03:27,783 --> 00:03:30,652
Do you eat hamburgers often?

49
00:03:30,652 --> 00:03:33,496
Yes. Almost every day.

50
00:03:33,496 --> 00:03:36,127
I told you, I live alone.

51
00:03:36,127 --> 00:03:38,809
Oh, why?

52
00:03:38,809 --> 00:03:42,080
My parents got divorced last winter.

53
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:45,950
So I just told them that I'd live alone.

54
00:03:47,344 --> 00:03:49,287
I see.

55
00:03:49,287 --> 00:03:50,222
Do you feel sorry for me?

56
00:03:50,222 --> 00:03:53,466
No, it's not that.

57
00:03:53,466 --> 00:03:55,544
It's just... I don't know what to say.

58
00:03:55,544 --> 00:03:56,803
I mean...

59
00:03:56,803 --> 00:03:59,413
If you live alone,

60
00:03:59,413 --> 00:04:02,241
you must feel bored when you eat.

61
00:04:02,241 --> 00:04:04,478
That's why I asked you to eat with me.

62
00:04:04,478 --> 00:04:06,329
Oh, right.

63
00:04:11,426 --> 00:04:13,828

64
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:19,917
I'll walk you home.

65
00:04:19,917 --> 00:04:22,471
What? Why so suddenly?

66
00:04:22,471 --> 00:04:26,833
My house is very far from here. It's about 40 minutes away.

67
00:04:26,833 --> 00:04:28,092
So?

68
00:04:28,093 --> 00:04:31,862
What do you mean? Your house is close by.

69
00:04:31,862 --> 00:04:35,842
 Too close to go home.

70
00:04:35,842 --> 00:04:38,642
Then you can come somewhere with me.

71
00:04:41,315 --> 00:04:43,826
 There's a lock inside, and it looks identical front and back.

72
00:04:43,826 --> 00:04:46,295
 Press it more than three times to reset it.

73
00:04:46,295 --> 00:04:49,114
 Press the password and pull down to open it.

74
00:04:49,114 --> 00:04:50,549
It's my first time playing the room escape game.

75
00:04:50,549 --> 00:04:52,409
I've played it a few times.

76
00:04:52,409 --> 00:04:53,810
- Doesn't it look fun? 
 - But...

77
00:04:53,810 --> 00:04:55,746
I think we'll fail. I don't think we'll be able to escape.

78
00:04:55,746 --> 00:04:57,680
Do you want to bet?!

79
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,416
- Okay, sure. 
   - Please wear

80
00:04:59,416 --> 00:05:01,484
 your eye masks and enter the room.

81
00:05:01,484 --> 00:05:03,812
Okay. I feel nervous.

82
00:05:03,812 --> 00:05:06,355
- Are you scared? 
 - Yes.

83
00:05:08,875 --> 00:05:10,259
What do we do?

84
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:11,478
I think we should remove the handcuffs.

85
00:05:11,478 --> 00:05:13,329
- The key... 
 - We should look here.

86
00:05:13,329 --> 00:05:15,416
Hey, what is that? Why is the key in there?

87
00:05:15,416 --> 00:05:17,935
Oh, it's right here.

88
00:05:17,935 --> 00:05:19,036
Look!

89
00:05:19,036 --> 00:05:20,495
Look. I found it!

90
00:05:20,495 --> 00:05:22,305
- It's in here. 
 - Yes.

91
00:05:22,305 --> 00:05:23,231
Hey!

92
00:05:23,232 --> 00:05:25,934
You're good at this. Wow!

93
00:05:25,934 --> 00:05:27,910
Thank you.

94
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:30,538
- This is number five, right? 
 - Yes.

95
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:34,026
We did it! What is this?

96
00:05:34,026 --> 00:05:36,002
Do you want to try?

97
00:05:36,912 --> 00:05:38,963
Hey! Bye.

98
00:05:40,332 --> 00:05:42,276
- Oh, my gosh! 
 - You're really not scared?

99
00:05:42,276 --> 00:05:45,186
- I'm not scared at all. 
 - Really?

100
00:05:45,186 --> 00:05:46,421
Stop it!

101
00:05:46,421 --> 00:05:48,865
What is this? Oh, gosh!

102
00:05:48,865 --> 00:05:51,902
 Since you escaped successfully, I'll take a Polaroid picture.

103
00:05:51,902 --> 00:05:54,029
 I'll take it on the count of three.

104
00:05:54,029 --> 00:05:57,530
